Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Kee Realty Wash

data.description: Cute ranch home located on almost half an acre on a canal with NO FLOOD INSURANCE! Beautiful kitchen updated in 2023 with new stainless steel appliances and hood fan, subway backsplash and cement countertops.  Additional updates include the full bath and laminate flooring throughout and freshly painted rooms.  An additional bonus room in the basement with a walk out, full bath and wood burning stove.  Detached garage has a loft, providing lots of storage.  The backyard has a deck and a firepit, perfect for entertaining.  There is also a pear and apple tree. Kitchen window order paid and to be replaced.  Canal is treated every year and is approximately 5-8ft deep in the summer.
